OL,3,CCity residents could face 15% council
OL,4,Ctax hike
OL,6,FA cash-strapped council is seeking
OL,7,Fgovernment permission to hike taxes on
OL,8,Fresidents by up to 15%.
OL,10,FBradford Council said it needed to
OL,11,Fmake "difficult decisions" as it seeks
OL,12,Fto save hundreds of millions of pounds
OL,13,Fover the next five years.
OL,15,FBosses have submitted a request to the
OL,16,Fgovernment to consider a council tax
OL,17,Frise of between 9.99% and 14.99%.
