OL,4,Ctax hike
OL,6,FAt the top end of the scale, the
OL,7,Fproposal would mean residents of band
OL,8,FA properties - which make up 40% of
OL,9,Fhomes in the district - would pay #170
OL,10,Fextra a year.
OL,12,FCouncil leader Susan Hinchcliffe said:
OL,13,F"We are trying wherever possible to
OL,14,Ffind new ways of working and new
OL,15,Ffunding sources so that we can save
OL,16,Fmoney without cutting vital services.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
