OL,3,CCity residents could face 15% council
OL,4,Ctax hike
OL,6,F"This decision to request a one-off
OL,7,Fincrease in council tax beyond the
OL,8,Fusual 4.99% has not been taken
OL,9,Flightly. We realise that no one wants
OL,10,Fto see an increase in council tax when
OL,11,Fother bills are also rising."
OL,13,FHow much would bills increase?
OL,15,FA council tax rise of more than 5%
OL,16,Fnormally triggers a referendum.
OL,18,FThe council's finances are in such a
OL,19,Fparlous state that it was given #220
OL,20,Fmillion of government funds to keep it
OL,21,Fafloat last year.
