OL,3,CCity residents could face 15% council
OL,4,Ctax hike
OL,6,FIt has set out a range of proposed
OL,7,Fcuts to services, venue closures and
OL,8,Fprice rises, as well as an increase in
OL,9,Fcouncil tax.
OL,11,FIt said it had identified #48.6m of
OL,12,Frevenue savings in 2024/25 with a
OL,13,Ffurther #43.6m of savings earmarked
OL,14,Ffor 2025/26.
OL,16,FBut councillors will hear that a
OL,17,Ffurther #50m of savings will need to
OL,18,Fbe made each year until 2030.
