OL,4,Ctax hike
OL,6,FBosses say council tax is #145 below
OL,7,Fthe national average for metropolitan
OL,8,Fdistrict councils and the lowest in
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire.
OL,11,FThey say a 14.99% rise would reduce
OL,12,Fthe need to borrow by #140 million
OL,13,Fover the next five years.
OL,15,FThe announcement comes after Bradford
OL,16,Flaunched its year as UK City of
OL,17,FCulture, a venture which is thought to
OL,18,Fbe costing the council about #10
OL,19,Fmillion.
