OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "By all of us
OL,7,Fpaying #3 or #4 pounds a week extra
OL,8,Fnow, we can avoid up to an additional
OL,9,F#140 million of borrowing that the
OL,10,FBradford council taxpayer will
OL,11,Fotherwise have to pay for in the
OL,12,Ffuture."
OL,14,FIt said support would be made
OL,15,Favailable to residents who struggled
OL,16,Fto pay.
