OL,6,FMs Hinchcliffe added: "Like many other
OL,7,Fcouncils, after 14 years of reductions
OL,8,Fin funding from central government we
OL,9,Fhave been left in an unsustainable
OL,10,Ffinancial position.
OL,12,F"We welcome the additional funding
OL,13,Ffrom the new government for next year.
OL,14,FIt shows they've listened and this is
OL,15,Fa significant step in the right
OL,16,Fdirection but it can't solve the
OL,17,Fchallenges local government faces
OL,18,Fovernight.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
