OL,6,F"We are still however facing severe
OL,7,Fpressures on budgets for all our
OL,8,Fservices, from social care to
OL,9,Fmaintaining our parks and green
OL,10,Fspaces. We will have to continue to
OL,11,Fmake difficult decisions to ensure a
OL,12,Fstable financial future."
OL,14,FA government spokesperson said: "As
OL,15,Fwith previous years the government
OL,16,Fwill consider requests for higher
OL,17,Flevels of council tax from councils
OL,18,Fseeking exceptional financial support,
OL,19,Fbut this government will put taxpayers
OL,20,Fat the forefront of any decision."
